### =============================================================
### PRODUCTS COLLECTION
### =============================================================

### GET ALL PRODUCTS
GET https://t9-store-project.onrender.com/products

### GET PRODUCT BY ID
GET https://t9-store-project.onrender.com/products/65f1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d1

### CREATE PRODUCT (Requires Login)
POST https://t9-store-project.onrender.com/products HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "category": "Electronics",
    "brand": "T9",
    "model": "SuperTab 10",
    "price": 299.99,
    "stock": 50,
    "description": "High-performance electronic tablet with 10-inch display.",
    "warranty": "1 year",
    "releaseDate": "2026-01-01"
}

### UPDATE PRODUCT (Requires Login)
PUT https://t9-store-project.onrender.com/products/65f1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d1 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "category": "Electronics",
    "brand": "T9",
    "model": "SuperTab 10 Pro Plus",
    "price": 399.99,
    "stock": 30,
    "description": "Ultimate tablet with upgraded storage and battery.",
    "warranty": "2 years",
    "releaseDate": "2026-01-01"
}

### DELETE PRODUCT (Requires Login)
DELETE https://t9-store-project.onrender.com/products/65f1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d1 HTTP/1.1


