### GET ALL REVIEWS
GET https://t9-store-project.onrender.com/reviews

### CREATE REVIEW (Requires Login)
POST https://t9-store-project.onrender.com/reviews HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "productId": "65f1a2b3c4d5e6f7a8b9c0d1",
    "userId": "user_rudy_99",
    "rating": 5,
    "comment": "Incredible value for the price. Fast shipping!",
    "date": "2026-04-15"
}

